headline: Free Geek Receives $300,000 Grant From KeyBank Foundation
summary: Grant will support Free Geek's program designed to narrow the digital divide and advance the fundamental digital skills needed to advance education, find and maintain jobs and access critical services PORTLAND, OR / ACCESS Newswire / October 2, 2025 ...
